What does that mean
[br][size=1]Posted at: November 15, 2006, 10:28:45 AM[/size][hr]Still cant edit. Can anyone tell me in detail. plz. Like tell witch folders to open and stuff. That would be great
[br][size=1]Posted at: November 15, 2006, 11:17:25 AM[/size][hr]Oh come on someone plz
[br][size=1]Posted at: November 15, 2006, 05:06:04 PM[/size][hr][quote author=shawn333171 link=topic=38465.msg463452#msg463452 date=1163625504]
I am using Testscape an i can’t figure out how to edit the lines to add things like monsters and stuff. Can anyone help. It would be very appreciated.
[/quote]

anyone plz

[/quote]

Go to “compile” press edit, delete everything and paste this in there

@echo off title yourservernamehere "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_09\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_09\bin\java.exe" server pause[/quote]

it says the system cannot find path specified now. the compiler worked find before and i want to know where to go to edit stuff like put monsters in.
